      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/12/5129",
      "text": [
        ": \"اَلْعَبْدُ إِذَا أَقَرَّ عَلَى نَفْسِهِ عِنْدَ اَلْإِمَامِ مَرَّةً أَنَّهُ سَرَقَ قَطَعَهُ وَ اَلْأَمَةُ إِذَا أَقَرَّتْ عَلَى نَفْسِهَا عِنْدَ اَلْإِمَامِ بِالسَّرِقَةِ قَطَعَهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5129 - Ali ibn Ri'ab narrated from Ḍurays Al-Kunasi from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) who said:\n\"If a male slave confesses to theft once before the Imam, his hand is to be cut off.\nLikewise, if a female slave confesses to theft before the Imam, her hand is to be cut off.\""
        ]
      }
    },
